reviewText:
Annie Oakley- great shooting!  Kit Carsen- fighting corruption in the west (nice buns)

Northwest Passage- features Star Trek cast member appearance, Bonanza cast member appearance, Beverly Hill Billies father is a regular cast member

Judge Roy Bean- a lot of fun to watch, unconventional judge who wears many hats and is a relentless pursuer of justice

Cowboy G men - government men enforcing the law in the west

Frontier Doctor- holds his own in the face of deceit encountered in his line of work in the west

Stories of the Century- Doc Holiday and other outlaw stories
